{"tid":356310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「女神」之路　欣宜Keep Fat上位","createTime":"2017-08-12T03:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T02:47:34.000Z","uid":89543,"like":3,"dislike":125,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b60c4529318f3b7c8139508fffcaf3f8c6b04e98","tid":356310,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:34:04.000Z","msg":"欣宜演藝事業發展順利，自出道以來，經常帶起不同話題，2003年她擔任瘦身代言人，由近230磅減至130磅，成為一時佳話！不過，她於2015年推出歌曲《你瘦夠了嗎？》，正式宣布做回自己，不再過節食減肥的日子，此舉令她人氣不跌反升，更被大讚夠真性情。同年她再化身重量級美人魚拍攝水中照片，獲讚肥得可愛。至2016年她憑《女神》一曲橫掃四大頒獎禮的歌曲獎項，並首奪「我最喜愛的女歌手」，人氣急升！<br />\n<br />\n除了樂壇成績亮眼，她唱而優則演，為多套電影擔任重要角色，包括2016年上映的《辣警霸王花》和今年上映的《29+1》，她於後者更擔正做女主角，演技備受讚賞。而2015年，她更開始經營曲奇餅生意，至今年6月在銅鑼灣開設實體舖，可謂瓣數多籮籮！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170812/photo/bkn-20170812000347637-0812_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170812005815\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170812%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170812000347637-0812_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170812005815&h=f12e9590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fdcd1dfaec08ad5cfa0af42b8f03073d0b83db6","tid":356310,"uid":132302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd3fac1c766485a60af691a37cdde6e78814ae4","tid":356310,"uid":89543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:38:07.000Z","msg":"誰偷偷留下負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34aa08b5877e90d7fd585cc0b3d184866c5ae83d","tid":356310,"uid":123224,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:41:55.000Z","msg":"留名等睇做愛圖"},{"pid":"5fa200dc5b65a5c0f1c92cf9cdfc133aa1419269","tid":356310,"uid":60764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:44:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b13be60e04fdc178f8a6ae4027d780731